review_blob: My father in law introduced me to this and its now my second favorite behind Dos Equis.
Dont like the aroma. It looks great in a glass but I do liked the appearance. Good beer
Love the gold look after pouring into a tall glass. Not the greatest aroma but its decent enough to drink. Great cheap beer. .. cant go wrong with that.
This is my go to beer. If Im having friends over this is in my cooler and my friends love it too.
Good beer. nice label plus goes down easy. Smells a little though but drinkable. Good
Cool name and bottle but not a great tasting beer. Not a huge Brown ale fan. Drinkable
beer_name: Big Sky Moose Drool Brown Ale
